Brother.

29
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:35,850
Why are you here?

30
00:01:35,870 --> 00:01:37,690
Your wedding with Your Highness is approaching.

31
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:38,670
As your elder brother,

32
00:01:38,690 --> 00:01:39,979
how could I not come to deliver the dowry?

33
00:01:40,789 --> 00:01:41,580
Yunze,

34
00:01:41,729 --> 00:01:42,979
regarding the royal wedding,

35
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,990
I'd like to have a private talk with Your Highness.

36
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,280
As the bride-to-be,

37
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:47,130
could you please

38
00:01:47,150 --> 00:01:47,870
give us a moment?

39
00:01:47,900 --> 00:01:49,370
