40
00:01:50,100 --> 00:01:51,460
Don't make things hard for His Majesty.

41
00:01:51,620 --> 00:01:52,259
Fine.

42
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:00,680
What's wrong?

43
00:02:00,940 --> 00:02:01,600
Your Majesty,

44
00:02:01,630 --> 00:02:02,910
something serious has happened.

45
00:02:02,930 --> 00:02:04,950
The Northern Rong has been frequently causing trouble on our border,

46
00:02:04,970 --> 00:02:06,830
using all kinds of strange poisons.

47
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:07,680
Now,

48
00:02:07,700 --> 00:02:09,949
half of Southern Yue's people are poisoned,

49
00:02:09,970 --> 00:02:11,180
and there's no cure.

50
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,820
But Northern Rong has never used poisons before.

51
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,290
That's what's suspicious.

52
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:16,600
It's clear that someone is using Southern Yue's poison-making techniques

53
00:02:16,630 --> 00:02:18,780
to cultivate even deadlier poisons.

54
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,090
Your Majesty,

55
00:02:20,170 --> 00:02:21,860
where's the mask

56
00:02:21,890 --> 00:02:22,570
my sister used to wear

57
00:02:22,590 --> 00:02:23,380
when she was with Jet Black Armored Cavalry?

58
00:02:24,010 --> 00:02:26,000
When Shisan was under Shang Kefeng's control and poisoned,

59
00:02:26,020 --> 00:02:26,980
the mask fell into Shang Kefeng's hands.

60
00:02:27,090 --> 00:02:28,270
That matches up.

61
00:02:28,290 --> 00:02:29,610
The border guards say

62
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:30,930
that the person leading the Northern Rong army

63
00:02:30,950 --> 00:02:32,420
is wearing a mask.

64
00:02:32,450 --> 00:02:34,000
We must not let Shisan know about this,

65
00:02:34,190 --> 00:02:35,990
or she will certainly risk her life alone

66
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:36,750
to fight against Shang Kefeng

67
00:02:36,770 --> 00:02:37,579
to the death.

68
00:02:37,890 --> 00:02:39,079
I was thinking the same thing.

69
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:40,250
Brother,

70
00:02:40,460 --> 00:02:41,300
after the royal wedding,

71
00:02:41,490 --> 00:02:42,660
I will personally lead the army

72
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:43,910
to help you defeat the rebels.

73
00:02:43,930 --> 00:02:45,910
Southern Yue and Northern Zhao are closely connected, 
one cannot live without the other.

74
00:02:45,940 --> 00:02:47,320
I can't thank you enough for such a big favor.

75
00:02:47,510 --> 00:02:48,160
You and I

76
00:02:48,300 --> 00:02:49,770
