77
00:02:52,130 --> 00:02:53,810
[Northern Border Battlefield]

78
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,610
General Han,

79
00:02:58,970 --> 00:03:00,830
the Northern Rong army launched a surprise attack on our camp,

80
00:03:00,910 --> 00:03:02,130
and their force was overwhelming.

81
